duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide person-centered counseling, advocacy, and case management for patients.
Develop treatment plans and meet agency documentation standards.
Strategically tailor effective clinical/case management services to meeting diverse patient needs.
Contribute to the success of MultiCare expectations and core values, continuously learning, and performing other duties as needed or assigned.

education_certification.credential: Master's degree in counseling or one of the behavioral sciences from an accredited college or university. At least two years of experience in direct treatment of persons with mental illness or emotional disturbance.
